{"tid":1603100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[10月1戰術討論]試下比d創意諗下有咩做?","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T06:53:09.000Z","uid":153673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d14cc3d8570de7826001da94e791fc505a74411a","tid":1603100,"uid":153673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"我屌撚曬你班傻閪連登仔淨係識拗分區搞定集中搞，完全冇人討論10月1有咩實際行動，近幾次出黎一係就鳩行到尾，一係就警民衝突，你唔煩我都厭啦。<br />\n<br />\n所以大家可唔可以比D奶力諗下到底10月1出到黎有咩搞，eg :雷射筆射穿&quot;支&quot;旗，砌下D大字賀佢老母，etc (鳩諗出黎屌得細力D)<br />\n<br />\n記住，中共係最撚要面，所以大家快手諗諗有咩計仔攞出黎賀佢老母，避免又警民衝突spin我地老母。<br />\n<br />\n利申:第一次開post，建議D淨係想屌鳩我既巴打直接上一頁<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"79514142def83573f931e16c107bca7a2d7b3a40","tid":1603100,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4238847000d6fb0c264896f6ce832214b1f2acb5","tid":1603100,"uid":64576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M9MyZDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM9MyZDM.jpg&h=97629d6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#攝衫<br />\n#tuckinyourshirt<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xeYhGZd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxeYhGZd.png&h=66b71668&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"303926b695896a649214652f79c62a60330eedf9","tid":1603100,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:14:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">前&hearts;線&hearts;B&hearts;B&hearts;需&hearts;要&hearts;你</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WEddZM3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWEddZM3.jpg&h=f62ae3bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"511285fb1d6e73e4cb31527a22698d13cdbd5179","tid":1603100,"uid":1